Package: predatortune
Version: 2.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libadwaita-1-0 (>= 1.2), libgtk-4-1 (>= 4.8), lm-sensors
Maintainer: Madhav <madhav@meowdev>
Description: Fan & thermal control GUI for Acer Predator laptops on Linux
 PredatorTune is a native GTK4/Adwaita thermal control application for Acer
 Predator laptops running Linux. It provides real-time temperature and fan
 monitoring, and performance mode switching via kernel platform_profile.
Homepage: https://github.com/0xshubhs/predatur
